 presence of nitrogen during processing plays a critical role in\ncontrolling hydride precipitation and subsequent SRF properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2018 17:27:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Sep 2018 01:42:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-14"}
