 tracking error down to 6.6 cm, in a\nflight volume that is roughly 18 m by 7 m and 3 m tall. We also demonstrate the\nrobustness of the controller by attaching a drag plate to the UAV in flight\ntests and by pulling on the UAV with a rope during hover.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2018 17:30:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 7 Jun 2020 01:23:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-09"}
