y allowed the radiative energy\nof the current outburst to propagate freely until terminating at the northern\nbow shock where it strengthened the masers. Additionally, water masers have\nbeen detected toward MM7 for the first time, and a highly-collimated CS (6-5)\noutflow has been detected toward MM4.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2018 21:37:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-24"}
